test_even_range:
assert [3, 4] == [-8, -10, -12]
  At index 0 diff: 3 != -8
  Right contains one more item: -12
  Full diff:
  - [-8, -10, -12]
  + [3, 4]
test_positive_range:
assert [3, 4] == []
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 3
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [3, 4]
test_large_range:
assert [3, 4] == []
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 3
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [3, 4]
